Review_Text: Great Documentary it has a lot of energy and backstory on the players to get a better look at their life's as players,students and boys becoming men
Very good show, highlights all the young talented players on the team.

Review_title: A tv show no one asked for
Review_Text:
This is what happens when your daddy buys you a tv show
And buys you a draft pick
The kid will end up a 5-5-5 average coming off the bench
But let's be honest prince james will pay off ESPN to hype up his son
The good news is bronny (silly name) looks to have inherited his pops hair line
Do yourself a favor and skip this show along with space jam 2.There's this amazing documentary about a GOAT called last dance now that is a show you must watch.I honestly do not know how a kid in HS that averages 8 points get a show, it's kind of annoying, is the kid going to surpass prince james ? No fn way, so what will he end up doing ? Being 2-8 in the finals ?? Come on.
